snippet.title: Vanquish on Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The HD remaster of VANQUISH is coming to PC on Steam, May 25, 2017!
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/460810/Vanquish/
https://www.platinumgames.com/official-blog/article/9298

HDでリメイクされた『VANQUISH』 (Steam PC版)が2017年5月26日に発売！(日本時間)
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/460810/Vanquish/
https://www.platinumgames.co.jp/magazine/detail/?id=2_12039
